<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Marie Fontaine — Créatrice Artisanale</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&family=Lato:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    /* ── Variables ── */
    :root {
      --beige:      #f5efe6;
      --beige-dark: #e8ddd0;
      --terra:      #c4633a;
      --terra-dark: #a84e2b;
      --green:      #4a6741;
      --green-light:#6b8f63;
      --brown:      #5c3d2e;
      --text:       #2e1f14;
      --text-light: #7a5c4a;
      --white:      #fffdf9;
      --radius:     12px;
    }

    /* ── Reset & Base ── */
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      background: var(--beige);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    img { max-width: 100%; display: block; }
    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }

    /* ── Utility ── */
    .container { max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }
    .tag {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--terra);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    }
    .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.15); }
    .btn-primary { background: var(--terra); color: var(--white); }
    .btn-secondary { background: transparent; color: var(--terra); border: 2px solid var(--terra); }
    .provisional { outline: 2px dashed var(--terra); outline-offset: 4px; position: relative; }
    .provisional::after {
      content: "✏️ texte provisoire";
      position: absolute;
      top: -22px; left: 0;
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--terra);
      background: var(--white);
      padding: 1px 6px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    /* ── NAV ── */
    nav {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      background: rgba(245, 239, 230, 0.92);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--beige-dark);
      padding: 16px 0;
    }
    nav .container {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .nav-logo {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--brown);
    }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 32px; list-style: none; }
    .nav-links a {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-light);
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--terra); }
    .nav-cta { display: block; }

    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .nav-links { display: none; }
    }

    /* ── HERO ── */
    #hero {
      min-height: 92vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: var(--beige);
    }
    .hero-bg {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 70% at 80% 50%, rgba(196,99,58,0.10) 0%, transparent 70%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 50% at 10% 80%, rgba(74,103,65,0.08) 0%, transparent 60%);
    }
    .hero-inner {
      position: relative;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 64px;
      align-items: center;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 80px 0;
    }
    .hero-text { }
    .hero-text h1 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 3.6rem);
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.15;
      color: var(--brown);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .hero-text h1 em {
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--terra);
    }
    .hero-text p {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: var(--text-light);
      max-width: 420px;
      margin-bottom: 36px;
    }
    .hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .hero-visual {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .hero-card {
      background: var(--white);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 40px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(92,61,46,0.12);
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 320px;
      width: 100%;
    }
    .hero-card .craft-icon {
      font-size: 4rem;
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .hero-card h3 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      color: var(--brown);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .hero-card p {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--text-light);
    }
    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      background: var(--green);
      color: var(--white);
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 780px) {
      .hero-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; padding: 60px 0; }
      .hero-visual { order: -1; }
      .hero-text h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; }
    }

    /* ── À PROPOS ── */
    #apropos {
      background: var(--white);
      padding: 100px 0;
    }
    .apropos-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 80px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .apropos-visual {
      position: relative;
    }
    .apropos-frame {
      background: var(--beige);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 60px 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .apropos-frame .avatar {
      width: 100px;
      height: 100px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--terra) 0%, var(--green) 100%);
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
    .apropos-frame .since {
      display: inline-block;
      background: var(--terra);
      color: var(--white);
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 6px 16px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .apropos-accent {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -20px;
      right: -20px;
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      background: var(--green);
      border-radius: 50%;
      opacity: 0.15;
    }
    .apropos-text h2 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.4rem);
      color: var(--brown);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }
    .apropos-text p {
      color: var(--text-light);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    .apropos-values {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 28px;
    }
    .value-chip {
      background: var(--beige);
      color: var(--brown);
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      border: 1px solid var(--beige-dark);
    }

    @media (max-width: 780px) {
      .apropos-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 48px; }
    }

    /* ── SERVICES ── */
    #services {
      padding: 100px 0;
      background: var(--beige);
    }
    .section-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 60px;
    }
    .section-header h2 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.4rem);
      color: var(--brown);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .section-header p {
      color: var(--text-light);
      max-width: 520px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .services-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 28px;
    }
    .service-card {
      background: var(--white);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 36px 28px;
      border-bottom: 4px solid transparent;
      transition: transform 0.25s, box-shadow 0.25s, border-color 0.25s;
    }
    .service-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-6px);
      box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(92,61,46,0.12);
      border-color: var(--terra);
    }
    .service-icon {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      display: block;
    }
    .service-card h3 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: var(--brown);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .service-card p {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--text-light);
      line-height: 1.65;
    }
    .service-card .price {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 18px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--terra);
    }

    @media (max-width: 860px) {
      .services-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 560px) {
      .services-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }

    /* ── TÉMOIGNAGES ── */
    #temoignages {
      background: var(--brown);
      padding: 100px 0;
    }
    #temoignages .section-header h2 { color: var(--beige); }
    #temoignages .section-header p { color: rgba(245,239,230,0.65); }
    #temoignages .tag { color: var(--terra); }
    .temoignages-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 24px;
    }
    .temo-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 32px 28px;
    }
    .temo-stars {
      color: #f5c842;
      font-size: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .temo-card blockquote {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      color: var(--beige);
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .temo-author {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .temo-avatar {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--terra);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .temo-name {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--beige);
    }
    .temo-location {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: rgba(245,239,230,0.55);
    }

    @media (max-width: 860px) {
      .temoignages-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 560px) {
      .temoignages-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }

    /* ── CONTACT BAND ── */
    #contact {
      background: var(--beige);
      padding: 100px 0;
    }
    .contact-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--terra) 0%, var(--terra-dark) 100%);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 72px 64px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 60px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .contact-text h2 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.4rem);
      color: var(--white);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }
    .contact-text p {
      color: rgba(255,253,249,0.75);
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .contact-details { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; }
    .contact-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      color: var(--white);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    .contact-item span:first-child {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      width: 28px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .contact-form-side {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 36px 32px;
    }
    .form-group { margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .form-group label {
      display: block;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255,253,249,0.75);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .form-group input,
    .form-group textarea {
      width: 100%;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      color: var(--white);
      font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      outline: none;
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
      resize: vertical;
    }
    .form-group input::placeholder,
    .form-group textarea::placeholder { color: rgba(255,253,249,0.4); }
    .form-group input:focus,
    .form-group textarea:focus { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }
    .btn-white {
      background: var(--white);
      color: var(--terra);
      font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      border: none;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      cursor: pointer;
      width: 100%;
      margin-top: 8px;
      transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-white:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); }

    @media (max-width: 780px) {
      .contact-box { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 48px 32px; gap: 40px; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .contact-box { padding: 36px 20px; }
    }

    /* ── FOOTER ── */
    footer {
      background: var(--brown);
      color: rgba(245,239,230,0.6);
      text-align: center;
      padding: 32px 24px;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
    }
    footer strong { color: var(--beige); font-weight: 700; }

    /* ── DIVIDERS ── */
    .wave-divider {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      overflow: hidden;
      line-height: 0;
    }
    .wave-divider svg { display: block; width: 100%; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- NAV -->
  <nav>
    <div class="container">
      <span class="nav-logo provisional">Marie Fontaine</span>
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="#apropos">À propos</a></li>
        <li><a href="#services">Services</a></li>
        <li><a href="#temoignages">Avis</a></li>
        <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
      </ul>
      <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary nav-cta">Me contacter</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section id="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-inner">
        <div class="hero-text">
          <span class="tag provisional">Artisan créateur · Normandie</span>
          <h1 class="provisional">Des créations <em>faites à la main</em>, avec cœur et savoir-faire</h1>
          <p class="provisional">Je crée des pièces uniques alliant tradition artisanale et sensibilité contemporaine, pour ceux qui aiment ce qui dure et ce qui touche.</p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="#services" class="btn btn-primary">Découvrir mes créations</a>
            <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-secondary">Me contacter</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-visual">
          <div class="hero-card provisional">
            <div class="craft-icon">🪴</div>
            <h3>Créations artisanales</h3>
            <p>Chaque pièce est réalisée à la main, en quantité limitée.</p>
            <div class="hero-badge">✦ Fait avec soin, depuis 2015</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- À PROPOS -->
  <section id="apropos">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="apropos-grid">
        <div class="apropos-visual">
          <div class="apropos-frame provisional">
            <div class="avatar">🧑‍🎨</div>
            <p style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif; font-size:1.1rem; color:var(--brown); margin-bottom:12px;">Marie Fontaine</p>
            <p style="font-size:0.85rem; color:var(--text-light); margin-bottom:16px;">Artisan créateur indépendant</p>
            <span class="since">Depuis 2015</span>
          </div>
          <div class="apropos-accent"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="apropos-text">
          <span class="tag">À propos</span>
          <h2 class="provisional">Passionnée par mon métier, attachée à chaque détail</h2>
          <p class="provisional">Bonjour, je m'appelle Marie. Depuis plus de 10 ans, je crée des pièces artisanales à la main, dans mon atelier normand. Mon travail est guidé par une conviction simple : ce que l'on fabrique avec soin a une âme.</p>
          <p class="provisional">Je m'inspire des matières naturelles, des formes organiques et du temps qui passe — pour offrir des objets qui accompagnent votre quotidien avec douceur et élégance.</p>
          <div class="apropos-values">
            <span class="value-chip provisional">🌿 Matières naturelles</span>
            <span class="value-chip provisional">✦ Fait main</span>
            <span class="value-chip provisional">♻️ Éco-responsable</span>
            <span class="value-chip provisional">💌 Sur commande</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICES -->
  <section id="services">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="tag">Services & Offres</span>
        <h2 class="provisional">Ce que je propose</h2>
        <p class="provisional">Des créations pour tous les goûts et toutes les occasions — du cadeau personnel à la commande professionnelle.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="services-grid">
        <div class="service-card">
          <span class="service-icon">🎁</span>
          <h3 class="provisional">Créations sur mesure</h3>
          <p class="provisional">Vous avez une idée, je lui donne forme. On discute ensemble de vos envies, des matières, des couleurs — et je crée une pièce unique rien que pour vous.</p>
          <span class="price provisional">À partir de 45 €</span>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <span class="service-icon">🛍️</span>
          <h3 class="provisional">Collection permanente</h3>
          <p class="provisional">Des pièces disponibles immédiatement, fabriquées en petite série. Idéales pour s'offrir ou offrir sans attendre.</p>
          <span class="price provisional">À partir de 20 €</span>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <span class="service-icon">🏢</span>
          <h3 class="provisional">Commandes professionnelles</h3>
          <p class="provisional">Cadeaux d'entreprise, dotations événementielles, décoration d'espace. Je m'adapte à vos besoins et vos délais.</p>
          <span class="price provisional">Sur devis</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TÉMOIGNAGES -->
  <section id="temoignages">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="tag">Témoignages</span>
        <h2>Ils me font confiance</h2>
        <p style="color:rgba(245,239,230,0.6);" class="provisional">Des clients satisfaits, des créations qui restent.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="temoignages-grid">
        <div class="temo-card provisional">
          <div class="temo-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <blockquote>« Un travail d'une qualité rare. La pièce commandée était exactement ce que j'avais imaginé, et même mieux. Je recommande sans hésiter. »</blockquote>
          <div class="temo-author">
            <div class="temo-avatar">👩</div>
            <div>
              <div class="temo-name">Sophie L.</div>
              <div class="temo-location">Rouen, Normandie</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="temo-card provisional">
          <div class="temo-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <blockquote>« J'ai commandé des cadeaux d'entreprise pour mon équipe. Résultat magnifique, livraison dans les temps et une attention aux détails vraiment touchante. »</blockquote>
          <div class="temo-author">
            <div class="temo-avatar">👨</div>
            <div>
              <div class="temo-name">Thomas B.</div>
              <div class="temo-location">Caen, Normandie</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="temo-card provisional">
          <div class="temo-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <blockquote>« Une artisane passionnée, à l'écoute et très réactive. J'ai adoré l'expérience de la création sur mesure. J'en reparlerai autour de moi. »</blockquote>
          <div class="temo-author">
            <div class="temo-avatar">👩</div>
            <div>
              <div class="temo-name">Claire M.</div>
              <div class="temo-location">Paris</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CONTACT -->
  <section id="contact">
    <div class="container">
